title: Authorities on scene of rollover crash on Plainview Dr.
content: TOLEDO (WTVG) - Authorities are currently on the scene of a rollover crash.    This happened just before 3:30pm Saturday on Plainview Drive near N. McCord Road.    Our reporter on the scene of the crash says this is not a deadly crash. We are still working to get more information from state troopers.    This is a developing story. Stick with 13abc as we continue to gather updates.
